@node "DYNAMITE DUX"
DYNAMITE DUX

Type in "CHEAT" on title screen and press any key 'F1' to 'F6' to skip to
respective level.  Or type "NUDE" to go straight to boxing sub-game.
@endnode

@node "DYNASTY WARS"
DYNASTY WARS

(Cheat #1)
When the title screen appears, type "CHEAT MODE".  From now on, press 'F2' to
skip to the next level.

(Cheat #2)
Pause the game with 'F9', then hold down 'SHIFT', '1' and 'HELP', followed by
unpausing the game with 'F10'. You will be able to skip levels by pressing
the 'F2' key.
@endnode
@node "DYTER-07"
DYTER-07

When the game loading screen appears, type in word "GIBB".  This activates
the cheat mode.  When 'W' is pressed you get extra weaponry and when 'S' is
pressed your shields are replenished.  'L' key ends level.
@endnode
